## What to generate

This project's cockpit scripts ship as **runnable placeholders** with annotated
`# ── CONFIGURE ──` blocks. Your job is to explore `@@APP_NAME@@` and fill them in:

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `tmux-cockpit.sh` | remote/k8s cockpit — log windows, port-forward, worker priming |
| `tmux-cockpit-local.sh` | local dev cockpit — backend window + workers |

Replace the `# ── CONFIGURE ──` defaults with the real values, then regenerate the
project-specific sections of the `e2e-cockpit` / `e2e-operator` overlays.

